{"tid":1067180,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)爸爸 霸吧 爸爸霸 霸吧 爸爸霸 霸吧 霸爸1-3","createTime":"2019-03-18T10:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T14:14:05.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"01ef53d5412e446d8de2af324269718152adb0cf","tid":1067180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=86aa51c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=10951c5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=7dae07c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/xT9DPpf0zTqRASyzTi/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FxT9DPpf0zTqRASyzTi%2Fgiphy.gif&h=c76575e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事講述貿易聯邦的紐特&middot;甘雷總督以抵制船舶稅為由對那卜星（Naboo）實行了封鎖。絕地大師魁剛&middot;金和歐比王&middot;肯諾比師徒在絕地議會命令下被派遣為使節與貿易聯邦談判，試圖化解衝突，然而，他們並不知道黑暗西斯尊主達斯&middot;西帝已經掌控了貿易聯邦。<br />\n紐特&middot;甘雷總督在得知前來的大使為絕地武士後，與達斯&middot;西帝聯繫，達斯&middot;西帝下令進攻那卜並殺死前來的魁剛&middot;金和歐比王&middot;肯諾比。紐特&middot;甘雷於是切斷那卜的對外通訊，並集結大批機器人軍隊侵略那卜，綁架了那卜女王佩咪&middot;艾米達拉。魁剛&middot;金和歐比王&middot;肯諾比在化解了紐特&middot;甘雷的追殺後<br />\n<br />\n2.時間位在《星際大戰首部曲：威脅潛伏》後十年，銀河中竄起一股獨立星系力量，由前絕地武士杜庫伯爵領導，試圖率領一部分星系分裂銀河共和國。那卜星參議員佩咪&middot;艾米達拉前往銀河共和國首都，參與反對建立共和軍的議案<br />\n<br />\n3.星系正處於複製人戰爭的硝煙之中，銀河共和國議長白卜庭被獨立聯邦的第二號人物&mdash;&mdash;格里弗斯將軍綁架。絕地武士安納金&middot;天行者和絕地大師歐比王&middot;肯諾比率領著一支小分隊展開營救。安納金在戰鬥中殺死了西斯大君杜庫伯爵（達斯&middot;提拉納斯），兩名絕地救出了白卜庭。他們想要逃離時卻被格里弗斯將軍俘獲。安納金和歐比王設法掙脫並加以還擊但格里弗斯將軍卻成功逃走，並將兩名絕地和議長困在格里弗斯將軍的旗艦惡意號（征服者級重巡洋艦）中。安納金被迫使船在科羅森的一條登機跑道上硬著陸<br />\n<br />\n8 20PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=637b1cce\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=d5426673\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1e68f991e93e9d7e5d814d7312fa73cd160a3a","tid":1067180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2bc8a4bdd2637e9af9762ad153fc09a1dc7a60","tid":1067180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"disli